boxcar-growl - Push notification to Boxcar for iPhone/iPad

Copyright(C) Sharl Morlaroll <sharl@hauN.org>

* License - Perl/Artistic

* Installation

1. Join Boxcar (http://boxcar.io/)
2. Write to ~/.netrc

machine boxcar.io
	login           EmailAddress
	password        Password

3. Let's try!

	$ boxcar-growl test "push to boxcar by boxcar-growl"

4. Done.
